parameters: Oh, welcome. It's rare to see a young lady come in.

Hello. Sorry for coming in unannounced. What kind of shop is
this...?

It's a shiatsu massage parlor. I get a bit nervous when
young ladies like you come in since most of my customers are
elderly.

Are your shoulders stiff? I can give you a discount right
now?
(Shiatsu, huh... It might be good for some rest...)\$
I'll take the best acupressure treatment (1000 mon needed)
一番いい指圧を頼む（１０００文必要）

Well then, since I'm here, I'd like to request a shiatsu
massage, please.

Oh, really? Alright then, lie down on that futon over there.
You can keep your clothes on, it's fine.

(I've been having some stiffness in my shoulders and back
lately. This is a good opportunity.)
--Karin paid 1000 mon and lay face down on the futon.\$

...Alright. The treatment is finished. How do you feel? Is
your body feeling better?

Ah... It was truly the best feeling... It's like I've been
reborn... All the stiffness in my body has been blown
away\I[15]

Ha ha ha! That's great to hear! If you liked my shiatsu,
make sure to come again.

Yes! I'll definitely come back when I feel fatigued
again\I[15]
Karin's strength and technique have fully recovered!
I'm sorry, but I have other things to do...
That's too bad. The shop is always open, so come by anytime.
Oh! Are you the one from the other time...?
It's Karin. Is your shop open today?

Yes, there are no other customers right now, so it's fine.
Are you here for a treatment again today?
お願いする\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]（１０００文必要）

Thank you, Karin-chan. Then, as usual, please lie down on
the futon.
--Karin paid 1000 mon and lay face down on the futon.

...I'm sorry. I have an errand to run today, so I'll come
back another time.
指圧師に話しかける\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]
Hello--I've come for another treatment today.

Whoa!? Karin-chan, is that you? I'm sorry about the other
day...!
Huh, Sensei... why are you so pale?

Well, you know, having sexual intercourse with a female
client during a massage... It would be bad if other clients
found out...
Ahaha. It's okay. I won't tell anyone, so please relax.

Is that so? That's a relief. So, shall we proceed with the
massage today?

(His gaze is already intense before starting the massage...
Is this really okay...)
--Karin lay face down on the futon.
指圧師に話しかける\c[10]【指圧師エンド】\c[0]

I'm sorry, but I'm swamped with customers right now. Please
come back another time.

Ahh...♪ That feels so good! Your acupressure is amazing,
sensei...!

The sensei at this shop is really good at acupressure. There
are always so many reservations.
